Rating: 4
This is an awesome dish--people keep begging me to make it again and again--and I do, with great pleasure!!! I wouldn't (and didn't) change a thing but I might try using ground veal next time just to eliminate the step of using the food processor. Last time I made it a day ahead and it was even better after sitting a day--which of course makes it the perfect dish for a dinner party. This is bound to become a family favorite and a lifelong keeper.

