Rating: 4
I doubled this recipe for a Tuscan dinner party (made it ahead and froze it, too). It was incredibly rich and delicious, but, to be fair, I used very rich homemade veal and chicken stock. The porcini flavor didn't come through very much, but it was still a fantastic ragu.